column2: b'@semodough 1/ $AUTL cheap here. CEO (Christian Itin) is ex Micromet, developed/sold Blincyto to $AMGN for $1B+. AUTO1 CR rate at 2X Blincyto (84% vs 44%) w/ similar safety. r/r ALL approval in 2022, will move to 1L, a $500M indication. MC at $450M, $170M cash (good to approval) looks cheap.'

b'$AUTL catalysts AUTO1 pivotal study,enroll 100 relapsed or refractory (r/r) adult acute lymphoblastic leukemia (ALL) subjects with top-line data expected by end-2021; rapid maturation of ALEXANDER study of AUTO3, which has pinpointed a recommended Phase 2 dose (RP2D) withkeytruda'
